{
  "text": "We compute the usual measures of precision, fraction of similar functions in R f over all functions in R f , and recall, fraction of similar functions in R f over all similar functions in the dataset. Moreover, we also compute the normalised Discounted Cumulative Gain (nDCG) [CITATION_1] :",
  "correct_citation": {
